mras 系統安裝步驟
=================
安裝 mras 系統
--------------
假設安裝在 d:\master_paper

安裝 ruby
---------
至網路上下載 ruby 1.8.6 並安裝

安裝 rake 0.8.4
---------------
於命令列輸入以下指令：

code.install rake
D:\master_paper>gem install rake
Successfully installed rake-0.8.4
1 gem installed
::

安裝 rails 1.2.3
----------------
於命令列輸入以下指令：

code.install rails 1.2.3
D:\master_paper>gem install -v=1.2.3 rails
Successfully installed rails-1.2.3
1 gem installed
::

啟動 mras:server
----------------
於命令列輸入以下指令：

code.啟動 mras:server
D:\master_paper>rake mras:server
(in D:/master_paper)
Gem::SourceIndex#search support for String patterns is deprecated
D:/master_paper/config/boot.rb:25 is outdated
java -classpath .;config;lib/java;lib/java/jars/antlr-2.7.5.jar;lib/java/jars/ar
q.jar;lib/java/jars/commons-logging.jar;lib/java/jars/concurrent.jar;lib/java/ja
rs/icu4j_3_4.jar;lib/java/jars/iri.jar;lib/java/jars/jena.jar;lib/java/jars/jena
test.jar;lib/java/jars/json.jar;lib/java/jars/junit.jar;lib/java/jars/log4j-1.2.
12.jar;lib/java/jars/stax-api-1.0.jar;lib/java/jars/wstx-asl-2.8.jar;lib/java/ja
rs/xercesImpl.jar;lib/java/jars/xml-apis.jar mras.Server
log4j:WARN No such property [conversionPattern] in org.apache.log4j.RollingFileA
ppender.
log4j:WARN No such property [conversionPattern] in org.apache.log4j.RollingFileA
ppender.
[MRAS Server]:server start in port 1729!
::

啟動網站系統
------------
於命令列輸入以下指令：

code.啟動網站 
D:\fhopecc\project\master_paper>ruby script\server
Gem::SourceIndex#search support for String patterns is deprecated
./script/../config/boot.rb:25 is outdated
=> Booting WEBrick...
=> Rails application started on http://0.0.0.0:3000
=> Ctrl-C to shutdown server; call with --help for options
[2009-09-29 10:52:30] INFO  WEBrick 1.3.1
[2009-09-29 10:52:30] INFO  ruby 1.8.6 (2007-09-24) [i386-mswin32]
[2009-09-29 10:52:30] INFO  WEBrick::HTTPServer#start: pid=316 port=3000
::

開啟網頁
--------
於 IE 輸入以下網址

http://localhost:3000
